'''poliomyelitis''' (''plural'' '''poliomyelitides''')

# {{pathology}} Acute infection by the [[poliovirus]], especially of the [[motor neuron]]s in the [[spinal cord]] and [[brainstem]], leading to muscle weakness, [[paralysis]] and sometimes deformity.

====Synonyms====
* [[infantile paralysis]]
* [[polio]]